div.p:
that the Lord would be pleased to
         grant her true and unfeigned repentance

         for her sins;

to give her remission and forgiveness
          through Jesus Christ her saviour; 
          to grant her faith in him, with the 
          sanctification of his Holy Spirit;
          and, at last, to glorify her in heaven, which petitions, said she, 'whosoever shall make for me, the Lord hear
            and grant the same'.
